Type: Package
Title: Deep Learning for General Purpose
Version: 1.0.4
Author: Rajesh Balakrishnan
Maintainer: Rajesh Balakirshnan <rajeshbalakrishnan24@gmail.com>
Description: Aims to provide simple intuitive functions to create quick
        prototypes of artificial neural network or deep learning
        models. In addition novel ensemble models like 'deeptree' and
        'deepforest' has been included which combines decision trees
        and neural network.
